{"tid":739473,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"關係ig hashtag呢樣嘢","createTime":"2018-07-12T06:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T01:00:44.000Z","uid":42932,"like":8,"dislike":219,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"fb0706c612959a357b5c8b229c703ac37d13880e","tid":739473,"uid":42932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:40:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/12/143719_41077b4b4cf6d1dda3eb42eb0cccbe82.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F143719_41077b4b4cf6d1dda3eb42eb0cccbe82.png&h=52c250cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多人都鍾意用個人hashtag幫自己整個相簿，如果account 係public嘅話其實就所有人都睇到。而hashtag原意就唔係為咗個人化，而係將唔同嘅post擺埋一齊。<br />\n<br />\nYoutube界紅人jadelamm 就因為hashtag俾人拎咗去宣傳用而十分嬲，大家覺得：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ：鬧得啱，啲shop根本唔應該拎人個hashtag嚟宣傳，因為佢個post同人哋兩母女根本無關。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ：ig世界根本冇自訂hashtag呢回事，你用得我用得，你冇權叫我delete hashtag。"},{"pid":"95da2f4966b35d65acb2233e1f34679e8a7d3411","tid":739473,"uid":90,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:41:44.000Z","msg":"Who?"},{"pid":"f62b8991aed7486557cf0a402c2f3e89a665948d","tid":739473,"uid":8867,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:42:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54f46ea52b102646731746d7aa6cea4587001a8d","tid":739473,"uid":173397,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:43:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff30104467fa50746ac81385e515515c658b86ad","tid":739473,"uid":140738,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:44:27.000Z","msg":"個tag又無註冊商標<br />\n<br />\n有咩唔用得"},{"pid":"e08864ebd1aef11ee85d5b0c146a13e2d1962f39","tid":739473,"uid":42932,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f62b8991aed7486557cf0a402c2f3e89a665948d","tid":739473,"uid":8867,"like":10,"dislike":2,"scor